# ğŸ“Œ 1. Introduction to PowerShell

## âœ… What is PowerShell?

* Cross-platform task automation solution by Microsoft
* Includes:

  * Command-line shell
  * Scripting language
  * Configuration management framework
* Built on **.NET Framework**
* Object-oriented â†’ returns structured objects instead of text
* Works on **Windows, Linux, macOS**

---

## ğŸ•°ï¸ History

* Early 2000s â†’ Developed by Microsoft engineer Jeffrey Snow
* Released in **2006**
* Designed to replace limitations of cmd.exe & batch scripting
* **PowerShell Core (2016)** â†’ Open-source & cross-platform

---

## â­ Why PowerShell is Powerful

ğŸ‘‰ Commands return **objects with properties & methods**
â¡ï¸ Enables advanced filtering, automation & system interaction

