# ğŸ” 5. Piping, Filtering & Searching

---

## ğŸ”— Piping

```powershell
Get-Process | Select-Object Name
```

ğŸ‘‰ Passes objects between commands

---

## ğŸ¯ Filtering (Where-Object)

```powershell
Get-Process | Where-Object {$_.CPU -GT 100}
```

### Operators

| Operator | Meaning       |
| -------- | ------------- |
| -EQ      | Equal         |
| -NE      | Not equal     |
| -GT      | Greater       |
| -LT      | Less          |
| -Like    | Pattern match |

---

## ğŸ›ï¸ Selecting (Select-Object)

```powershell
Get-Process | Select-Object Name, CPU
```

---

## ğŸ” Searching (Select-String)

```powershell
Select-String "error" logfile.txt
```

ğŸ‘‰ Similar to grep / findstr
ğŸ‘‰ Supports Regex

